---
title: Mild Thai Red Veggie Curry with Jasmine Rice & Roasted Cashews
description: Enjoy a bowl of rich and creamy Thai red curry, loaded with colourful veggies and aromatic spices. With a sprinkling of roasted cashews to finish it all off, this delicious meal will beat your local takeaway joint!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mild-thai-red-veggie-curry-c6f872ee.jpg
